Info

class src.lidarToGeo.ept_info.Info(data)[source]

This class takes in the ept.json and processes the data in the json file to a format that we can easily call as attributes of the class

reference: https://entwine.io/entwine-point-tile.html

Attributes

Info.bounds

reads the data in the bounds key in the ept json

Info.conforming

reads the data in the boundsConforming key in the ept json

Info.datatype

reads what type of data format the point clouds are in

Info.hierarchytype

reads the data in the hierarchyType key in the ept json

Info.schema

reads the data in the schema key and passes that data to the Schema class

Info.span

reads the data in the span key in the ept json

Info.srs

reads the data in the 'srs' key and computes a CRS from the 'wkt' value in the 'srs' key

Info.version

reads the data in the version key in the ept json

Info.length()

reads the data in the points key in the ept json i.e all the data points in this particular data
